<item>
            <title>[LU-16544] kernel update [RHEL7.9 3.10.0-1160.83.1.el7]</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-16544</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Security Fix(es):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: memory corruption in AX88179_178A based USB ethernet device. (CVE-2022-2964)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;hw: cpu: LFENCE/JMP Mitigation Update for CVE-2017-5715 (CVE-2021-26401)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;Bug Fix(es):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Prevent unnecessary resets - Avoid leaving shost-&amp;gt;last_reset with stale value if EH does not run (BZ#2128337)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;i40e: Request to backport upstream commit 2e5a20573a92 (BZ#2129248)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;disable VMA-based swap-in readahead on PowerPC (BZ#2142455)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://access.redhat.com/errata/RHSA-2023:0399&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://access.redhat.com/errata/RHSA-2023:0399&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
